<P>Title: "Eighty-Fifth Day, Tuesday, 3/19/1946, Part 24", in Trial of the Major War Criminals Before the International Military Tribunal. Volume IX. Proceedings: 3/8/1946-3/23/1946. [Official text in the English language.] Nuremberg: IMT, 1947. pp. 501-504.</P>

