<P>Full Text:</P>

<P>MR. JUSTICE JACKSON: And one further question. It was also reported to you, was it not, in that report-I refer to Page 11:</P>

<P>"The public down to the last man realize that political drives, like those of 9 November, were organized and directed by the Party, whether this is admitted or not. When all the synagogues burned down in one night, it must have been organized in some way and can only have been organized by the Party."</P>

<P>That also was in the report of the Supreme Party Court, was it not?</P>

<P>GOERING: I have not found it yet. It is not the same page as mine.</P>

<P>MR. JUSTICE JACKSON: Let us find it and not have any mistake about it. Page 11. I should think it would be at the very bottom of Page 10, perhaps, where it starts.</P>

<P>GOERING: Yes, I have just found it.</P>

