<P>Title: "Eighty-Sixth Day, Wednesday, 3/20/1946, Part 17", in Trial of the Major War Criminals Before the International Military Tribunal. Volume IX. Proceedings: 3/8/1946-3/23/1946. [Official text in the English language.] Nuremberg: IMT, 1947. p. 539.</P>

<P>Author: International Military Tribunal</P>

