<BR CLEAR=ALL>

<h2>Arizona and the Death Penalty</h2>

Arizona allows the death penalty as an option in cases of first-degree murder where there at least one of 10 aggravating circumstances.
<P>
The sentence is death by lethal injection.<P>
Minimum age for capital punishment: none<p>
Executions 1930-1976: 41<P>
Executions since 1977: 4<p>


