<h2>Delaware and the Death Penalty</h2>

Delaware allows the death penalty as an option in cases of first-degree murder with aggravating circumstances.
<P>
The sentence is death by lethal injection.<P>
Minimum age for death penalty: none<p>
Executions 1930-1976: 15<P>
Executions since 1977: 8<p>
