<h2>Idaho and the Death Penalty</h2>

Idaho allows the death penalty as an option in cases of first-degree murder and aggravated kidnapping.
<P>
The sentence is death by lethal injection or firing squad.<P>
Minimum age for death penalty: none<p>
Executions 1930-1976: 3<P>
Executions since 1977: 1<p>

