<h2>Indiana and the Death Penalty</h2>

Indiana allows the death penalty as an option in murder cases which are accompanied by at least one of 13 aggravating factors.
<P>
The sentence is death by lethal injection.<P>
Minimum age for death penalty: 16<p>
Indiana forbids the execution of the mentally retarded.<P> 
Executions 1930-1976: 43<P>
Executions since 1977: 3<p>

