<BR CLEAR=ALL>

<h2>New Jersey and the Death Penalty</h2>

New Jersey allows the death penalty as an option in cases of purposeful or knowing murder and cases of contract murder.<P>
The sentence is death by lethal injection.<P>
Minimum age for death penalty: 18<p>
Executions 1930-1976: 74<P>
Executions since 1977: 0<p>
<P>
<BR><P>


