<h2>Oregon and the Death Penalty</h2>

Oregon allows the death penalty as an option in cases of aggravated murder.
<P>
The sentence is death by lethal injection.<P>
Minimum age for death penalty: 18<p>
Executions 1930-1976: 19<P>
Executions since 1977: 0<p>
