<h2>Utah and the Death Penalty</h2>

Utah allows the death penalty as an option in cases of aggravated murder.
<P>
The sentence is death by firing squad or by lethal injection.<P>
Minimum age for death penalty: none<p>
Executions 1930-1976: 17 <P>
Executions since 1977: 5<p>

