<h2>Wyoming and the Death Penalty</h2>

Wyoming allows the death penalty as an option in cases of first-degree murder, including both premeditated and felony murder.
<P>
The sentence is death by lethal gas.<BR><P>

<HR WIDTH=525 ALIGN=LEFT>
