<h2>The Military and the Death Penalty</h2>

The death penalty is a possible consequence of a conviction by a court martial in cases of murder and espionage.
<P>
The sentence is death by lethal injection.<BR><P>

<HR WIDTH=525 ALIGN=LEFT>
<IMG SRC="/graphics/ctv/headers/rights2.gif" ALT="Copyright 1996 by American Lawyer Media, L.P. All Rights Reserved.">
